{"tid":2159761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侵：大選投票若廣泛以郵遞方式進行將令美國成笑柄","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T16:27:44.000Z","uid":308915,"like":67,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"fd23c0d834fb5ddf64951b3bfa16f3461be41599","tid":2159761,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:40:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543996-20200816.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543996-20200816.htm&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=67fa3320\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543996-20200816.htm&h=e22a80c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543996-20200816.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-08-16 HKT 15:21<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普再批評郵遞投票，指11月總統大選若廣泛採用這種投票方式，將令美國淪為「笑柄」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，全面郵遞投票的首要問題，是有可能遺失選票，令大選結果可能要幾個月，甚至幾年才揭曉，因此永遠無法知道選舉幾時真正結束。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普一直反對郵遞投票，認為會導致選舉不公平，令民主黨總統候選人獲益。郵政署早前去信各州，警告數百萬張大選郵寄選票，可能未能趕及點算。<br />\n<br />\n郵政署新任署長被指是特朗普的忠心支持者，輿論批評署方專登減慢郵政服務。有專家指出，美國的郵遞投票系統安全，軍方亦有採用。"},{"pid":"6023e2c88d1f4d9861dba7ac6780be70057b6342","tid":2159761,"uid":16057,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"其實選總統用一個咁兒戲既方法去投<br />\n好難怪佢有咁既反應"},{"pid":"d15d59e25725b21ea486bbf92e5ab27a7178f0a0","tid":2159761,"uid":126731,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"方便支那幫手種票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb4739a68f644cae93fee26ab377e5c94b245bb","tid":2159761,"uid":1430,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"咁其實依家比唔比用郵寄選票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴撚線咁兒戲美國等玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces